high_descs: Turn around from where you are and then keep turning left until you are facing the coffee table
Pick up the newspaper from off of the coffee table
Turn around and turn to your left so you are facing the white sofa
Put the newspaper down on to the white sofa
Turn around to the TV stand behind you
Pick up the newspaper from the TV stand
Turn around again to face the white sofa
Put the other newspaper down on to the white sofa to the left of the other one
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on to the sofa

high_descs: Turn around and go to fireplace.  Turn left and left again to face a coffee table.
Pick up newspaper from bottom left and corner of coffee table, to the left and below the banana.
Turn left three times and face in the direction of the couch.
Place the newspaper on the couch near the arm of the couch.
Turn to the right and go to the tv stand.
Pick up the newspaper from the left of the tv on the tv stand.
Turn around and go the couch.
Place the newspaper on the couch, to the left of the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fireplace, then go left to the table in front of the couch.
Pick up the newspaper that is closest to you on the table.
Turn to the white couch to the right of the table.
Put the newspaper on the right side of the couch.
Turn around and go to the table with the TV on it.
Pick up the newspaper that is on the table to the left of the TV.
Turn around go to the white couch.
Put the newspaper on the couch to the left of the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on a couch.
